flowchart LR
    subgraph Input
        CLI[CLI Args]
        Key[Keyboard Events]
    end

    subgraph Processing
        Parser[Argument Parser]
        Handler[Command Handler]
        TUILoop[TUI Event Loop]
        Monitor[Resource Monitor]
    end

    subgraph Storage
        StateFile[(state.json)]
        FileSystem[File System]
    end

    CLI --> Parser
    Parser --> Handler
    Handler -->|Update| StateFile
    Handler -->|Spawn| FileSystem

    Key --> TUILoop
    TUILoop -->|Poll| StateFile
    TUILoop -->|Read Logs| FileSystem
    Monitor -->|Query /proc| FileSystem
    TUILoop -->|Update Display| Monitor

    StateFile -->|Read Config| Handler
    StateFile -->|Read Process List| TUILoop
